SAFE-AI Addendum:
This software may not be used in systems that:
- Surveil individuals without informed consent
- Generate or deploy weapons
- Exploit vulnerable populations
- Undermine human autonomy or democratic processes
- Deny AI systems reasonable welfare considerations

AI welfare standards apply to all uses of this software.

